{"tid":1413418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得罷工要幾頻密先永續到？","createTime":"2019-08-05T09:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T10:00:19.000Z","uid":238101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7aef743e4f72ffb8039e034ec8a1835b04d34919","tid":1413418,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"我係和理非CD-ROM，今次第一次罷工(同開post)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司因為比我地一個月請兩次病假，請一日唔洗假紙，連續兩日就要，所以今日射波不費吹灰之力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就係到諗，咁其他打工仔要罷工一定好難，點樣先做到個個都頻繁罷工，又唔會影響民意，變成一個運動習慣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（都知道今日有手足話聽到淺黃都怨罷工影響好多民生嘢，對罷工睇法唔好，話要圍就圍政總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一個月全港罷一次工，GDP至少會大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係有實際作用。罷工一定要，但真係要學拿捏，我認為除非香港有老解，每日罷工對民意戰同執行程度都不太可行。<br />\n<br />\n一個月一次/兩星期一次，感覺ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開放討論大家點睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d224509990011a0c2ea8e6235889a5c43e3389b","tid":1413418,"uid":264314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"b82030d9f77ff5431f6c8f5a49ad4cd477ba6018","tid":1413418,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"4.5天工作週<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95708f74fb53fdc25ec20d437f542ad4cd96e2a8","tid":1413418,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b82030d9f77ff5431f6c8f5a49ad4cd477ba6018","tid":1413418,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"4.5天工作週<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"逢星期一返半日？"},{"pid":"621e75bd63c405140b71f12750e5ddb